## 读取指定cookie

### 构建工具包，传入要搜索的名称，以及Cookie数组

```java
public class CookieUtils {
    public static Cookie readCookieByName(String name , Cookie[] cookies){
        //判断传入的参数是否正确
        if(name == null || name.isEmpty() || cookies == null || cookies.length == 0){
            return null;
        }
        for (Cookie cookie : cookies) {
            if(name.equals(cookie.getName())){
                return cookie;
            }
        }
        return null;
    }
}
```

#### 获取指定cookie信息

```java
public class ReadCookieByNameServlet extends HttpServlet {
    @Override
    protected void doPost(HttpServletRequest req, HttpServletResponse resp) throws ServletException, IOException {
        //得到指定的 cookie 的 value
        //1.先得到浏览器携带的所有 cookie
        Cookie[] cookies = req.getCookies();
        //2.使用工具类获取指定的 cookie
        String name = "username";
        Cookie cookie = CookieUtils.readCookieByName(name, cookies);

        if(cookie != null){
            System.out.println("cookie name = " + cookie.getName() + "\tvalue = " + cookie.getValue());
        }else{
            System.out.println("未找到该 cookie");
        }
    }

    @Override
    protected void doGet(HttpServletRequest req, HttpServletResponse resp) throws ServletException, IOException {
        doPost(req , resp);
    }
}

```

